1
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:39,060
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:39,060 --> 00:00:41,270
=Episode 3=

3
00:00:42,333 --> 00:00:43,500
From now on, you are

4
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:44,875
female Jinyiwei officers

5
00:00:45,208 --> 00:00:47,708
of the Northern Bureau.

6
00:00:52,875 --> 00:00:54,208
But remember this.

7
00:00:55,041 --> 00:00:56,000
You have no official posts,

8
00:00:56,333 --> 00:00:57,125
no formal status,

9
00:00:57,875 --> 00:01:00,416
and many won't even know you exist.

10
00:01:01,166 --> 00:01:01,958
You are nothing more

11
00:01:02,416 --> 00:01:05,000
than shadows of the Jinyiwei.

12
00:01:06,541 --> 00:01:07,291
Yes.

13
00:01:08,166 --> 00:01:10,166
I have high hopes for you.

14
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,250
(Jinyiwei Squad Leader
of the Left Qianhu Office)

15
00:01:12,250 --> 00:01:12,833
Thank you, my lord.

16
00:01:20,625 --> 00:01:22,000
Don't tease my bird too much.

17
00:01:22,416 --> 00:01:23,208
Yes, Young Master.

18
00:01:28,500 --> 00:01:29,041
Chang Beiming.

19
00:01:31,291 --> 00:01:32,500
What is your connection to Lu Guokai?

20
00:01:36,625 --> 00:01:38,458
I know Lu Guokai didn't want me in.

21
00:01:39,375 --> 00:01:40,625
You must have said something

22
00:01:41,458 --> 00:01:42,500
to make him change his mind.

23
00:01:43,333 --> 00:01:44,250
Who exactly are you?

24
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,083
How can a few casual words from you

25
00:01:46,083 --> 00:01:47,916
sway a Commissioner's decision?

26
00:01:52,416 --> 00:01:53,291
Lu Guokai

27
00:01:54,083 --> 00:01:54,791
owes me money.

28
00:01:56,791 --> 00:01:57,583
I threatened him.

29
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,125
If he didn't let you in,

30
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:00,875
he had to pay me back at once.

31
00:02:03,916 --> 00:02:04,750
Do all you men

32
00:02:05,708 --> 00:02:08,125
handle things this carelessly?

33
00:02:08,583 --> 00:02:09,625
I was helping you.

34
00:02:15,333 --> 00:02:16,291
Either way,

35
00:02:16,833 --> 00:02:17,750
you helped me again.

36
00:02:18,708 --> 00:02:19,375
In the martial world,

37
00:02:19,375 --> 00:02:20,291
we repay every favor and grudge.

38
00:02:20,291 --> 00:02:21,291
Name your price.

39
00:02:29,875 --> 00:02:30,458
Really?

40
00:02:31,125 --> 00:02:31,625
Yes.

41
00:02:44,375 --> 00:02:45,625
Go on one date with me,

42
00:02:46,250 --> 00:02:48,458
and we'll call it even.

43
00:02:53,416 --> 00:02:54,208
A date?

44
00:02:56,833 --> 00:02:57,625
What are you laughing at?

45
00:02:58,458 --> 00:03:00,916
You don't even know what a date is?

46
00:03:03,250 --> 00:03:04,583
I grew up in a Taoist temple.

47
00:03:05,125 --> 00:03:06,333
I rarely dealt with people.

48
00:03:06,875 --> 00:03:07,875
That's why I'm asking.

49
00:03:08,958 --> 00:03:11,000
(If she finds out what a date means,)

50
00:03:11,541 --> 00:03:13,125
(with that temper of hers,)

51
00:03:13,541 --> 00:03:16,000
(she will beat Chang Beiming up.)

52
00:03:16,791 --> 00:03:18,541
(Why not help things along?)

53
00:03:20,083 --> 00:03:21,125
A date?

54
00:03:22,125 --> 00:03:23,125
It's just

55
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:25,458
a perfectly ordinary social call.

56
00:03:26,208 --> 00:03:28,125
Two people dress up

57
00:03:28,333 --> 00:03:30,583
and meet at an agreed place.

58
00:03:31,333 --> 00:03:33,708
Then they eat, drink,

59
00:03:33,708 --> 00:03:34,958
and enjoy the sights.

60
00:03:39,541 --> 00:03:42,166
(Go with the Flow)
Xintian, Bingfan, from now on,

61
00:03:42,541 --> 00:03:43,500
we're sisters

62
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:44,833
eating from the same bowl.

63
00:03:45,458 --> 00:03:46,916
Come on. Drink up.

64
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:49,166
From now on, we share fortune

65
00:03:49,166 --> 00:03:50,333
and face hardship together.

66
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:51,291
Cheers.

67
00:03:51,291 --> 00:03:51,916
Well said.

68
00:03:56,375 --> 00:03:58,416
I'm so happy today.

69
00:03:58,708 --> 00:04:00,416
Not just because I joined the Bureau,

70
00:04:03,166 --> 00:04:05,666
but because I met two sisters

71
00:04:05,666 --> 00:04:07,083
who help me and care for me.

72
00:04:07,541 --> 00:04:08,625
A toast to you both.

73
00:04:08,625 --> 00:04:10,041
What about a toast to me?

74
00:04:12,875 --> 00:04:13,458
Young Master Chang?

75
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:20,708
Young Master Chang,

76
00:04:20,708 --> 00:04:22,041
that seat is mine.

77
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:28,875
Young Master Chang,

78
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:31,041
this is a girls' gathering.

79
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:33,083
What is a grown man like you

80
00:04:33,375 --> 00:04:34,708
doing here?

81
00:04:36,041 --> 00:04:38,208
You only passed an entry test,

82
00:04:38,625 --> 00:04:39,625
and you're this happy?

83
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:41,750
Still better than someone

84
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:42,916
who couldn't even pass it.

85
00:04:43,791 --> 00:04:45,791
Fan, don't hit below the belt.

86
00:04:46,458 --> 00:04:47,375
Don't call me that.

87
00:04:52,458 --> 00:04:53,125
There's something

88
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:54,291
I want to

89
00:04:55,125 --> 00:04:55,916
ask of you.

90
00:04:56,250 --> 00:04:56,958
Ask me?

91
00:04:58,666 --> 00:05:00,166
Can you move me to another room?

92
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:02,500
One with better soundproofing.

93
00:05:02,708 --> 00:05:03,291
Why?

94
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:05,083
Secret.

95
00:05:14,708 --> 00:05:15,458
Fine.

96
00:05:15,958 --> 00:05:16,541
But

97
00:05:17,208 --> 00:05:19,583
after work at the Bureau every day,

98
00:05:20,208 --> 00:05:20,916
you'll serve me

99
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:24,000
as my personal maid for two hours.

100
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:25,416
You...

101
00:05:26,416 --> 00:05:27,833
You're asking me for a favor,

102
00:05:27,833 --> 00:05:29,125
and you're still glaring?

103
00:05:30,166 --> 00:05:30,750
Give me a smile.

104
00:05:36,208 --> 00:05:36,708
This one.

105
00:05:40,291 --> 00:05:40,708
Well?

106
00:05:41,708 --> 00:05:42,500
Quiet and elegant.

107
00:05:43,708 --> 00:05:44,750
Who lives next door?

108
00:05:48,125 --> 00:05:48,541
You?

109
00:05:49,125 --> 00:05:49,666
What?

110
00:05:51,166 --> 00:05:52,166
In all of Chong'er Pavilion,

111
00:05:52,666 --> 00:05:55,333
my room is obviously the best.

112
00:05:55,333 --> 00:05:57,500
Thick walls. Great soundproofing.

113
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:06,640
(Late Lord Shen Lian)

114
00:06:08,833 --> 00:06:11,833
Father,
I have entered the Northern Bureau.

115
00:06:12,083 --> 00:06:13,875
May your spirit watch over me.

116
00:06:14,583 --> 00:06:17,375
I will uncover the truth
as soon as possible,

117
00:06:17,958 --> 00:06:18,875
expose the traitor,

118
00:06:19,458 --> 00:06:20,458
kill Leng Xin myself,

119
00:06:21,541 --> 00:06:23,083
(Late Lord Shen Lian)
and avenge you.

120
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:33,970
(Phantom Thief Feng Fuliu,
No. 2 on the Bounty List)

121
00:06:38,708 --> 00:06:39,333
Feng Fuliu.

122
00:06:42,083 --> 00:06:43,291
Feng Fuliu, stop right there!

123
00:06:49,416 --> 00:06:50,208
Feng Fuliu.

124
00:06:55,666 --> 00:06:56,708
Congratulations, Miss Shen,

125
00:06:57,333 --> 00:06:59,166
on joining the Jinyiwei Northern Bureau.

126
00:07:06,708 --> 00:07:07,500
A cup of wine

127
00:07:08,041 --> 00:07:08,750
to show my respect.

128
00:07:12,833 --> 00:07:13,458
What?

129
00:07:14,458 --> 00:07:16,333
Are you afraid

130
00:07:16,875 --> 00:07:17,500
it's poisoned?

131
00:07:19,416 --> 00:07:20,416
Who exactly are you?

132
00:07:22,166 --> 00:07:22,791
Me?

133
00:07:23,833 --> 00:07:25,541
Just a wanderer passing through.

134
00:07:26,416 --> 00:07:27,166
Then do you know

135
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,875
the first thing I'll do as Jinyiwei

136
00:07:30,333 --> 00:07:31,416
is bring you in?

137
00:07:32,958 --> 00:07:34,208
To be on a beauty's mind

138
00:07:35,166 --> 00:07:36,083
is one of the great honors

139
00:07:36,791 --> 00:07:37,875
of my life.

140
00:07:46,666 --> 00:07:47,583
I drank your wine.

141
00:07:47,791 --> 00:07:48,875
Now I'm taking you in.

142
00:07:50,791 --> 00:07:51,750
Bold and direct.

143
00:07:52,666 --> 00:07:53,500
Just as expected.

144
00:08:05,791 --> 00:08:06,458
(Miss.)

145
00:08:06,833 --> 00:08:08,041
(You look pretty when you smile.)

146
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:11,125
(You know,
you look nice when you smile.)

147
00:08:14,041 --> 00:08:15,416
(I ranked first in the written exam)

148
00:08:16,500 --> 00:08:17,458
(but failed the physical test.)

149
00:08:18,125 --> 00:08:18,958
(Feng Fuliu.)

150
00:08:19,208 --> 00:08:20,041
(Chang Beiming.)

151
00:08:21,708 --> 00:08:22,458
(It can't be.)

152
00:08:23,333 --> 00:08:23,750
(His fighting skills)

153
00:08:24,375 --> 00:08:25,291
(are terrible.)

154
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:30,430
(Leisurely and Free)

155
00:08:42,375 --> 00:08:44,416
(How does he look this good every time?)

156
00:08:47,583 --> 00:08:50,375
(Why is my heart beating so fast?)

157
00:08:53,291 --> 00:08:56,041
Young Master Chang,
where are you off to?

158
00:08:57,583 --> 00:08:58,625
Well...

159
00:08:59,208 --> 00:09:00,500
Isn't it obvious?

160
00:09:03,333 --> 00:09:04,833
I hope Bingfan

161
00:09:05,208 --> 00:09:07,416
will understand your devotion.

162
00:09:08,250 --> 00:09:09,625
She's not made of stone.

163
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,541
I offered my heart

164
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:15,625
to...

165
00:09:30,625 --> 00:09:31,125
Let's go.

166
00:09:32,375 --> 00:09:34,083
You brought your blade?

167
00:09:36,458 --> 00:09:37,083
Let's go.

168
00:09:45,666 --> 00:09:46,458
The Jinyiwei are here!

169
00:09:46,458 --> 00:09:47,083
Jinyiwei!

170
00:09:47,083 --> 00:09:48,083
Go, go!

171
00:09:48,583 --> 00:09:49,416
Jinyiwei!

172
00:09:49,416 --> 00:09:50,333
The Jinyiwei are here!

173
00:09:56,458 --> 00:09:57,125
Jinyiwei!

174
00:09:57,916 --> 00:09:58,625
Cover me!

175
00:09:59,666 --> 00:10:00,458
I need this too!

176
00:10:01,583 --> 00:10:02,458
Give it back.

177
00:10:02,708 --> 00:10:04,958
You wore your uniform on a date?

178
00:10:06,916 --> 00:10:08,500
Doesn't it look more proper?

179
00:10:09,208 --> 00:10:10,500
Don't you know? When Jinyiwei appear,

180
00:10:10,791 --> 00:10:11,958
everyone runs for cover.

181
00:10:13,541 --> 00:10:14,750
Are you trying
to clear the whole street?

182
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:17,958
Let go!

183
00:10:17,958 --> 00:10:18,875
No!

184
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,208
Let go!

185
00:10:20,208 --> 00:10:21,416
Give it to me!

186
00:10:22,125 --> 00:10:22,916
Then I'll go back and change.

187
00:10:22,916 --> 00:10:23,500
No need.

188
00:10:23,833 --> 00:10:24,666
I'll take you somewhere.

189
00:10:24,666 --> 00:10:25,166
Give it back!

190
00:10:25,166 --> 00:10:25,625
Let's go.

191
00:10:27,125 --> 00:10:28,333
That dress is nice.

192
00:10:28,333 --> 00:10:29,375
If you like it, I'll buy it.

193
00:10:29,375 --> 00:10:30,666
Look. A female Jinyiwei officer!

194
00:10:34,708 --> 00:10:35,375
Officer,

195
00:10:35,583 --> 00:10:37,125
my shop obeys the law.

196
00:10:37,333 --> 00:10:38,291
We are honest citizens.

197
00:10:38,625 --> 00:10:41,166
We have never done anything illegal.

198
00:10:42,333 --> 00:10:43,708
What are you doing? Don't bow to me.

199
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:46,333
We're here to buy clothes.

200
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:48,958
Pick out something suitable for her.

201
00:10:51,583 --> 00:10:53,291
Choose anything you like.

202
00:10:53,625 --> 00:10:54,625
Anything at all.

203
00:10:55,666 --> 00:10:57,125
You choose. Anything that suits her.

204
00:10:57,625 --> 00:10:59,041
And dress her up properly.

205
00:11:01,958 --> 00:11:02,541
Officer,

206
00:11:02,875 --> 00:11:03,458
right this way.

207
00:11:06,291 --> 00:11:07,333
Why are the Jinyiwei here?

208
00:11:07,333 --> 00:11:08,166
No idea.

209
00:12:08,291 --> 00:12:10,291
Is this all right?

210
00:12:12,708 --> 00:12:14,500
A beauty like you belongs in heaven.

211
00:12:16,041 --> 00:12:17,375
Why would you

212
00:12:18,875 --> 00:12:19,833
come down to earth for me?

213
00:12:36,890 --> 00:12:40,060
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

214
00:12:40,430 --> 00:12:43,810
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

215
00:12:44,060 --> 00:12:47,060
♪My heart drifted lost♪

216
00:12:47,060 --> 00:12:50,470
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

217
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:54,770
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

218
00:12:55,180 --> 00:12:58,520
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

219
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:01,310
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

220
00:13:01,310 --> 00:13:05,350
♪I've softly let it go♪

221
00:13:05,350 --> 00:13:09,220
♪The vow you made was true♪

222
00:13:09,220 --> 00:13:12,970
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

223
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:15,180
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

224
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:19,720
♪And forget at world's end♪

225
00:13:20,020 --> 00:13:21,520
♪Embracing memory♪

226
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:23,890
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

227
00:13:23,890 --> 00:13:27,770
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

228
00:13:27,770 --> 00:13:30,100
♪I wish to let it pass♪

229
00:13:30,100 --> 00:13:35,100
♪And run toward this vast life♪

